Egg-Catcher Game

  • Home

    • Project information

    This is an gaming application developed using python and tkinter, In this game initially user would be given 3 lives, after starting the game the user have to catch the eggs dropping down with the bowl.
    The player would be awarded score based on the count of eggs the player catches and if the player drops the egg then one life would be deducted for each egg. After all the lifes are comleted the game ends and the final score will be displayed.

The rules of this game are that a person selects a column and drops his token to the last possible, then the other player does the same, when one person has all the 4 tokens in a row that is from top to bottom or left to right or in any diagonal the person wins.
